  "text": "Here, C is the concentration of the diffusing substance, x the space coordinate measured normal to the section, and D the diffusion constant. In this work, a two-step diffusion method has been applied similar to that demonstrated by Gerstl et al. [CITATION_1] . This involves creating a step function in the normalised concentration of the 18 O isotope laterally in the film, such that the boundary conditions and solution to Eq. 1 are given by Eqs. 2.",
